<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #2563eb;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .otp-box {
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .timer {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .instructions {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #1565c0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #856404;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîê HireHub Verification</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello <%= fullName || 'User' %>,</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for signing up for HireHub! To complete your profile creation, please verify your email address using the OTP below:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-box">
                <%= otp %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timer">
                ‚è±Ô∏è This OTP expires in 100 seconds
            </div>
            
            <div class="instructions">
                <strong>üìã Instructions:</strong>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Enter this OTP in the verification dialog on your screen</li>
                    <li>Do not share this OTP with anyone</li>
                    <li>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email</li>
                    <li>If the OTP expires, you can request a new one</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning">
                ‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Security Notice:</strong> Never share your OTP with anyone, including HireHub support staff. We will never ask for your OTP.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The HireHub Team</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #bbb;">¬© 2025 HireHub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
